#    keyword whole \{ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ\}\[0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ_abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz\]# brightwhite
